title: Blow Your Balls OFF | Sal & Chris Present: Hey Babe! | EP 11
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!


This episode the Babes talk Chris has Turophobia aka a fear of cheese, boys announce our flavor of peanut butter is coming to Saratoga Peanut Butter soon, Chris doesn’t know cheese at all, the babes talk Super Bowl and Tom Brady, Tom Brady is the oldest player in NFL, Sal has a crazy story about Aaron Rodgers, The rapper Drake DM’d chris by accident thinking he was Chris Delia, Chris got booked on a hell gig and they meant to book Chris Delia, the babes have their balls blown off by a story, Sal trolls Chris’ dad, Joe Exotic vs Dog the bounty hunter, a quick history of siegfried & Roy, Chris’ lawyer is the guy from the goonies, people can now verify their house, Sal has a bad snack, do you cut mold off food and eat around it?, crazy weird facts about women during pregnancy, chris has a WILD story about his first born, what is mold, chris hurts his finger in england, Sal curses guys GET OVER IT!, Shout out Edie Falco and Kathrine Narducci, the babes try to figure out what’s going on with Game Stop, The time Chris got Paula Abdul’s number, Impractical Jokers is back!, Chris announces that he has a new series coming to TruTv.


Rate us on iTunes! Follow us on social media @HeyBabePod
